{"id":232707938,"title":"失眠寫詩／記憶","content":"🖼️\n\n-\n\n一炷香裊然離散的滅寂\n我再失去幾分鐘的消息\n存在與否的辯題\n不要染指撲朔\n也不要唾棄迷離\n\n望入隕石墜著的蛙仍安躺井底\n安躺井底半夢半醒\n枕間的谷半夢半醒\n蕩然如長音\n\n如我一直代謝著啊那些再重要的事情\n再重要的訊息\n再重要的\n……\n\n\n-\n\n🎞️","excerpt":"️，-，一炷香裊然離散的滅寂，我再失去幾分鐘的消息，存在與否的辯題，不要染指撲朔，也不要唾棄迷離，望入隕石墜著的蛙仍安躺井底，安躺井底半夢半醒，枕間的谷半夢半醒，蕩然如長音，如我一直代謝著啊那些再重要","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-17T20:02:32.551Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T03:48:25.919Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["失眠寫詩"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"Achi","department":"achi1996","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}